    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hue name for the range of colors intermediate between red and white, often a pale red, sometimes with a slight purple or yellow tinge.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
